{"tid":1912493,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"升升跌跌港股實戰記錄（1）","createTime":"2020-03-06T06:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T17:27:59.000Z","uid":93138,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"607877a0db581c839bfc61e0d0d640780d2efc9b","tid":1912493,"uid":93138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:19:11.000Z","msg":"我係一個趨勢策略者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個人都話港女好難玩<br />\n但我就覺得港股快起上黎勁過美股<br />\n（選股當然有條件）<br />\n所以暫時我都係鐘意玩港女<br />\n輸贏我都會報<br />\n報輸既出黎都係會令到我個心法更加穩定<br />\n遲啲都會有意拍下youtube分享下一啲技術手法心法<br />\n配上兩三張之前既股票圖，有晒買賣點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b9A6ZS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb9A6ZS4.jpg&h=379654ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J9KrZS3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ9KrZS3.jpg&h=4fc8b915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NoNX6x2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNoNX6x2.jpg&h=044e86ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實倉就睇番反應再報比大家，我自己以家實倉有3-4隻股的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ebcdc594f01c76d28e4ec17fd964556e933ebf","tid":1912493,"uid":93138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:23:42.000Z","msg":"之後前輸有3690 ，但因為我買既係牛仔所以就報唔到比大家<br />\n仲有輸過AMD <br />\n其他唔記得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a6ca54232b4419cb639a088ee0117f3cfe5d12","tid":1912493,"uid":93138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T08:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SZP0kAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSZP0kAV.jpg&h=5ab7085b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日跌6xx點，都係冇咩事"},{"pid":"1ec5597e82cd5e9574b01d8cab777f4b6627f7b9","tid":1912493,"uid":16664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbb42cdf9b5dbb121179b77d522427e37d97a04","tid":1912493,"uid":93138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T03:13:06.000Z","msg":"補番<br />\n<br />\n我裏面其餘個2隻都係輸錢走嫁，得果隻係賺25％up走左，不過最高峰係賺4x％，但都令我再進步左<br />\n不過我都輕視左呢場股災大戰<br />\n<br />\n以家我做緊既係反手沽到佢落美股地獄<br />\n本身想用期權，一見到個引伸波幅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果大家想以家追沽就建議咪搞，好可能夾死無命賠<br />\n非預測，因為我唔想預測<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為預測係賭鬼先會做<br />\n但我又會教大家用賭鬼既方法同數學方式去令到你笑到最後<br />\n<br />\n彈番先會加沽<br />\n（策略問題，但要double confirm，止蝕近咁推佢落地獄 ）"},{"pid":"97b246d1247e425b2bb9d3cdb7e525a7f89ea225","tid":1912493,"uid":14605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:27:14.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"56305f0d540b93f557648e619d456fa891e75723","tid":1912493,"uid":93138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:54:07.000Z","msg":"因為呢個星期學緊FX ,真心有D難<br />\n冇咩時間睇咁多股票<br />\n<br />\n前日暫時沽空左uber同埋少少PUT ,因為我覺得值博,因為止蝕大約8%<br />\n暫時博中左<br />\nPUT 就唔好買,因為個鍋升得太貴 唔值買<br />\n今次買跌好明顯遲左同反應慢左,好後悔<br />\n算啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好成日諗撈底<br />\n因為5號已經係一個活生生既例子,你想你個本金玩完你可以試下<br />\n記住你D時間都係錢黎<br />\n(你撈中個底又如何,代表佢下一個牛市佢會升咩????)<br />\n錯既事就係錯,唔好去堅持<br />\n<br />\n例子:<br />\n條女送左頂綠色野比你,你仲會唔會諗佢會改過?<br />\n緊係飛左佢4百4先啦   (當然佢變好之後又可以番番去試一試佢咩料<br />\n係出面(大市)慢慢搵番一條又令女性格又好既女<br />\n再計劃下溝唔溝到同點溝(值博率)<br />\n如果出面(大市)呢期出產成班豬閪,咁你搵中豬閪機會都好大,<br />\n或者都真係比你搵中一個令女,佢都好大機會係一個一落左妝好豬既女人<br />\n<br />\n當出面(大市)呢期出產番D令女或者豬排同令女均等既時候<br />\n咪又再出黎搵過食囉!!<br />\n<br />\n我自己玩左咁耐股牛熊全部都未試過溝<br />\n輸左就算啦.......<br />\n<br />\n我唔分享沽空,難好多,因為出場真心難"},{"pid":"2f4d095fc32448b84ee89a57daa15fdfbc6e4680","tid":1912493,"uid":93138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"都係沽慢左嫁啦<br />\n因為個市好神經刀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ba5nC36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fba5nC36.jpg&h=44d31ae3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"257634dbf189441136f97adbf44e91002d4c9aa6","tid":1912493,"uid":93138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hw71T1U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHw71T1U.jpg&h=fdff6395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國hsbc跌得仲慘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3f460eb9e966ba7cb72ba020f3df69cb45919d","tid":1912493,"uid":212825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"Lm 巴打可唔可以分享點揀港股，由其是咁多妖股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：港股只敢買大藍籌"},{"pid":"29e72444f5cf9a80228f0c45a655cd3fec9cdf76","tid":1912493,"uid":93138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d3f460eb9e966ba7cb72ba020f3df69cb45919d","tid":1912493,"uid":212825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"Lm 巴打可唔可以分享點揀港股，由其是咁多妖股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：港股只敢買大藍籌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:25:12.000Z","msg":"我反而係香港唔鍾意玩大股(藍籌 市值大既股)(妖股垃圾8字頭都唔玩)<br />\n因為就我自己經驗個所謂既大股D莊成日睇住個止蝕黎做,跌爆你再升過<br />\n<br />\n首先大藍籌係一個迷思黎<br />\n1.就算係咩股都係可以跌到pk(唔理你咩市值大咩,大藍籌)<br />\n藍籌唔代表你穩陣,因為佢只不過係指數成份股<br />\n呢個5號2318明顯到比你睇到<br />\n當然有D勁操控既700果D唔講啦<br />\n同埋美股都有晒版你睇<br />\n(~~~~但港女好似冇咩咁來來回回,但一睇市寛就知到晒~~~~~)<br />\n<br />\n2,揀股 <br />\n我係睇sma同BB去搵既 <br />\